quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"M wẽen ne ãdg t'a sã n wa lʋɩ."
  53,2,"Yãmb tũud-n-taagã pa menme, a pa kedg me ye."
  53,3,"A pa gomd a yõor yamleoog me ye."
  53,4,"Rẽndame tɩ yaa wahɩ sẽn tʋmse."
  53,5,"Pãn-kεgeng soab (a Gibriilã) n tɑɑ-a ɑ nengẽ."
  53,6,"Nɑɑnd sẽn be neerã, t'ɑ be ɑ yɑlẽ wã tɩ yɑɑ vẽeneg tɩ nɑbiyɑɑmã ne-ɑ."
  53,7,"T'a be yĩngr-yĩngri."
  53,8,"Rẽ poorẽ t'a (Gibriilɑ) pẽneg n sig n kolge."
  53,9,"Tɩ yaa wala tãp ne a to sʋk vɩʋʋgo, ma sẽn paood n pa ta rẽ."
  53,10,"T'ɑ togs Wẽnd yɑmbɑ Mʋhɑmmɑd, bũmb ning A sẽn tʋms-ɑ t'ɑ tɑɑsã."
  53,11,"Nɑbiyɑɑmã sũurã pa yag bũmb ning a sẽn yã wã ye."
  53,12,"Rẽ yĩnga, yãmb wẽeda ne-a no-koεεm bũmb ning a sẽn yã wã zugu?"
  53,13,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, a leb n yã-a lame yiib-n-soaba."
  53,14,"Tɑɑb-tεk Mugnugẽ wã (yaa tɩɩg sẽn be saasẽ wã n yaa rʋʋd fãa tεk zĩiga)."
  53,15,"Ma'awaa Arzãnã bee beenẽ ( (lallg zĩig Arzãn) ma (gãag zĩig arzãna) )."
  53,16,"Wakat ning sẽn wa n sigd Sɩdratã(tɩɩgã) zugã, sẽn yɑɑ Wẽnd sɑgellã, bũmb ning sẽn pɑtɑr to wã."
  53,17,"Nɑbiyɑɑmã ninfrã pa wẽnege, a pa kedg me."
  53,18,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka a yãa a Soabã yel-soalem bεd-bεdã sãnda."
  53,19,"Rẽ yĩnga yãmb tẽedame tɩ rʋbsã ɑ Laat ne a ʿƲzzaa?"
  53,20,"La a Manaat sẽn yaa tãaben-soabã nafdame?."
  53,21,"Yãmb n tar roapã yãmb sẽn nong-b rãmbã, tɩ Yẽ yaool n tar pagbã yãmb sẽn pɑ kisb rãmb n pɑ rɑt-bɑ?"
  53,22,"Ad rẽnda yaa zãmb pʋɩɩb moasã wae!"
  53,23,"B pa yɩ rẽnda yʋy bala, yãmb sẽn pʋde, yãmb ne y saam-rãmba, Wẽnd pa sik tagmas a yĩng ye. B sẽn tũudã pa yɩ rẽnda sãmbg lɑ b yõyã yɑm-leedo. La sɩd la hakɩɩka, kãndgr waa bãmb nengẽ sẽn yi b Soabẽ wã."
  53,24,"Bɩ ninsaal paamda a sẽn tẽed lɑ ɑ saagdẽ wã tɩ rʋbsɑ n sugs-ɑ lɑme wã?"
  53,25,"Rẽnd yaoolem la rãeenem (Lɑɑhrã ne Dũni wã) bee ne Wẽnde t'A kõt ɑ sẽn rɑt-ɑ."
  53,26,"La sõor waoog malεgs sẽn be saasẽ wã, tɩ b susg pa nafd ba fʋɩ rẽnda Wẽnd sẽn kõ sor poore, A sẽn rat-a soaba la A yardẽ."
  53,27,"Ad neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne yaoolem raarã, bãmb pʋtɑ malεgsã pog-yʋy."
  53,28,"La bãmb pa tar bãngr ne rẽnda ye, b sẽn tũudã pa yɩ rẽnda sãmbg bala, la ad sãmbg pa tõe n gɩgd sɩd ba fʋɩ."
  53,29,"Bɩ f ball n bas ned ning sẽn gũt-a a kuidg n yit Tõnd yʋʋrã tẽegre, n pa rat sã n pa Dũni vɩɩmã."
  53,30,"Rẽ la b bãngrã tεka, ad fo Soabã n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn menem-a n yi A Sorã zugu, Yẽ n leb n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn kãndg-a."
  53,31,"La Wẽnd n so bũmb ning sẽn be saasẽ, la sẽn be tẽng zugu, bʋɩl yĩng t'A na rol neb nins sẽn wẽng-bã b sẽn tʋmã, la A rol neb nins sẽn maneg-bã ne manegre."
  53,32,"Neb nins sẽn zãagd zunuub-bεdã la yel-beedã ralla zunuub-bõonesã, ad fo Soabã yaa yaaf-yaleng Soaba, Yẽ n mi yãmb n yɩɩda, wakat ning A sẽn wa n yẽbg yãmb n yi Tẽngẽ wã, la wakat ning yãmb sẽn wa n yaa bõn-vɩʋʋs n be yãmb ma-rãmbã pʋse, bɩ y ra pẽg y mens ye, Yẽ n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn zoet-a Wẽnde."
  53,33,"La rẽ yĩnga fo pa yã ned ning sẽn gõd a kuidga?"
  53,34,"La a kõ bilfu, la a monge?"
  53,35,"A tara bãng soaandag tɩ yaa yẽ n ne bɩ?"
  53,36,"Bɩ b pa kõ-a kɩbar ne bũmb ning sẽn be a Muusa gafẽ wã,"
  53,37,"La a ɭbraahɩɩm sẽn pids a pʋlengã?"
  53,38,"Tɩ ned fãɑ pa na n tʋk a to zunuub ye."
  53,39,"La pa be ne ninsaal ralla a sẽn tʋmã."
  53,40,"La a tʋʋmã b na yã."
  53,41,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ b roal-a rol-pidsdga."
  53,42,"La yaa fo Soabẽ wã la tεk zĩiga."
  53,43,"La yell sẽn yalẽ, Yẽ n kɩt tɩ b laadẽ la A kɩt tɩ b kũmdẽ."
  53,44,"La yell sẽn yalẽ, Yẽ n kʋʋd la A vɩɩmsde."
  53,45,"La yell sẽn yalẽ, A naana kõbg a yiibã: rao la paga."
  53,46,"Sẽn tũ ne mani wakat ning a sẽn wat n kiigdẽ wã."
  53,47,"La ad yẽbg-zẽngã bee ne Yẽnda."
  53,48,"La yel sẽn yalẽ, Yẽ n maan rakãaglem la A leb n kõ arzεka."
  53,49,"La yell sẽn yalẽ, Yẽnda la Sɩʿɩraa Soabã (yaa ãdg yʋʋre tɩ zɩdbã rɑ tũu-ɑ)."
  53,50,"La yell sẽn yalẽ, A halka rẽenem ʿAadã (ɑ Hʋʋd nebã)."
  53,51,"La a Ṯamuud, la A ka kell ye."
  53,52,"La a Nuuh nebã hal pĩnda, ad bãmba, bãmb ra yɩɩme n yɩɩd ne wẽgd la kengre."
  53,53,"La a Mutafɩkaat (a Lʋʋt neba), A kibind-b lame."
  53,54,"Tɩ bõr-ba, bũmb ning sẽn bõr-ba."
  53,55,"La yaa fo Soabã neema bʋgo la f maand sika?"
  53,56,"Yãoã yaa bugsd sẽn wõnd bugsdbã sẽn reng tɑɑrã buudu."
  53,57,"Pẽnegdã (Dũni yikrã) pẽnegame."
  53,58,"A pa tar pãrgda, zẽng tɩ pa Wẽnd ye."
  53,59,"Gom kãngã la yãmb maan yel-soalmã?"
  53,60,"La y laadẽ, n pa kũmdẽ?"
  53,61,"Tɩ yãmb yaa sẽn wɩsde."
  53,62,"Bɩ y maan suguud n kõ Wẽnde, la y tũ-A."
